short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: CXone Agent Click to Dial Extension

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: NICE inContact Click-to-Dial Extension makes placing calls effortless for Agents. This extension converts +E164 phone numbers into clickable links that allow seamless dialing from any webpage using the NICE CXone Agent application.
